    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS SPICER - REMOVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>REMOVE</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
            <title>SHIFT LEVER ASSEMBLY (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302302">Figure 2</hotlnk>)
            </title>
            <figure id="f1302302" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1302302" filename="../figg13/G1302302.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 2. Shift Lever - Exploded View</caption>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove six bolts. Separate the shift tower from the transmission.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Cut the tie down straps and lift the boot off the lever.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Holding the lever in a vise, remove the tower snap ring.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Pull the lever, the upper and lower plastic sockets, and the two opposing springs from
                    the tower.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
